Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:04.30,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,200)}行方すら知らぬまま
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.98,in_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fad(100,200)}天と地も見失い
