Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎之插班生 風斬冰華並非人類
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是由AIM擴散力場所產生的物理現象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 是我們的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.92,0:00:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭啥啊 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.45,0:00:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你哭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只會讓人覺得噁心罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來讓你久等了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經...可以放心了

Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:32.29,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(655,85)}{\fscx92}#23{\fscx100\b0} 風斬冰華
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:32.29,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,400)\pos(735,69)\fs14\fscy94}<朋友>
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.06,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 太不像話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.46,0:02:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別因為這點無聊事就流眼淚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.06,0:02:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.66,0:03:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡欣雀躍吧 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界對你還算不賴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少還是有那麼一個笨蛋珍惜你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.79,0:03:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不只我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題問得太沒水平了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這用得著什麼理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是跟他們說了一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「救救我的朋友」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你見識到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.87,0:03:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所居住的這個世界 還是有救贖的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我要告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的容身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:03.30,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(454,440)}<幻想>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不會因為這點程度 就輕易地破滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲 殘殺他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.69,0:04:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個都不能少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.65,0:04:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配置B 最優先確保市民安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「如神之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.11,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<Michael>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神之藥」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:37.47,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<Rephael>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神之力」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:38.98,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<Gabriel>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「神之火」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:39.85,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<Uriel>
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示四界的四天之象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將正確力量引領到正確方向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正確配置加正確的引導
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這地步都還是預想當中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說在最壞打算當中這點讓我不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.40,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年 你是真的想幹一場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算覺得膽怯 誰也不會責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看到了吧 我右手的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.15,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過「不得不幹」才是正確答案呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「幹一場」是指...那個...幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎 當然是去阻止那頭怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 強自己所難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然月詠老師都有些好學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:36.95,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(414,440)}<Preparation>
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.95,0:05:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count 5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣絕對沒活路的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.01,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.99,0:05:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.15,0:05:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別阻止我 風斬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的右手對異能之力 會不論善惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切力量打消
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定也不會例外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count 1
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們不能相互觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的朋友這點 也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 是「一定」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回...來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.37,0:06:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 下次我們再帶上Index
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起去個什麼地方玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Count 0
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.22,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.05,0:07:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你也沒辦法逃走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有逃跑的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子TM才用不著逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫就給我閉上嘴 躺著好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就將這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想弄第二隻出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次是不能同時保持兩隻的存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 只要靈活地利用那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情也是辦得到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.91,0:08:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 讓她跑掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明目標就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然輕易就逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回想一下 我有沒有什麼地方沒考慮到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英國清教？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟Index同屬一個組織的人 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要發起戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要一個火種
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須讓大量的人知道我乃英國清教的手下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小鬼 是叫什麼來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 我也不一定非得殺掉那個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉你也沒問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.98,0:09:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Index嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 你這衣服是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼熱的天 還穿這種衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.69,0:09:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在風颼颼地透著過 挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 只是用扣針固定著罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要穿這種勁爆的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心靈有許多過去的創傷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要太過深究
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 他還真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.37,0:10:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我覺得那個魔術師好像是盯上了冰華
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,術式也帶著英式風味
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的沒事倒還好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫「冰華」的 是跟你們在一起的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這次可不是当麻拉過來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我先碰到她的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「這次」...呢 ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好擔心好擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我也擔心一個女孩子被留在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是讓当麻跟女孩子在那種幽暗的環境下獨處也讓我很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是毫無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你就不擔心他的安全嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当麻？這個不用擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為無論發生什麼事 他也絕對會回到我身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「回到你身邊」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.65,0:10:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道那傢伙跟她...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 史芬克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就留在這裡 你快點去抓了貓再回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.77,0:11:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是容易被貓討厭的體質
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算追也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你這麼做 我真的很感激
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史芬克斯 喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼地下街的封鎖還沒解除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地下街的管理單位 跟我們的管轄單位不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.15,0:11:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要解除封鎖 還需要多一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.56,0:12:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 說來 你身體沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻石像應該不會再來攻擊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個黑褐色的哥特loli女並不是逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是開始追獵下一個目標罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的目的並不是殺掉我或者風斬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要特定的條件都齊全了 她殺誰都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.20,0:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都可以？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 其中一個就是...Index
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.37,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣 但是如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.87,0:12:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託那些人 讓他們確保她的人身安全的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Index並不是這座城市的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被警備員發現了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.83,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,440)}<Antiskill>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能會被逮捕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能貿然請他們確保她的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只能從這裡走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 如果間隔牆打開了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能輕易地趕在那混蛋前面了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我就要落得如此被動的局面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.69,0:13:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要一個人去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Index現在有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.62,0:13:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不去 我也有救她的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓怪物 去當怪物的對手就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然 我不認為自己 能贏得了那隻石像怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少我能當誘餌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我被打的間隙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子就能逃命了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怪物 能做的只有這種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你怎麼還說這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不是什麼怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:22.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說 這麼做 你認為我會開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我覺得這樣做值得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甘願做一隻怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是怪物 無論被那隻石像打多少次 也死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是怪物 我才有膽子去直面那隻石像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用我的力量 去保護我重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:48.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我很慶幸 自己是隻怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風斬...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風斬！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.27,0:15:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 不是沒事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風斬冰華
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有重量 也沒有空氣的流動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由能力者們所放出的AIM擴散力場所製造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陽炎之街
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟學園都市存在於同一位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常人卻看不見的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條陽炎之街
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我去看了 就給了別人予任務
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.85,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我有了想法以後 就會讓某人的人生出現了偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任務是「發條」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這個社會 這麼大的一個精密機器 注入生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為「發條」的一個零件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.24,0:17:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法出去外頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算看到「外頭」的事物跟人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.40,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都無法觸碰以及跟他們攀談
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那時是我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功出到了外頭的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.81,0:17:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得按鍵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.76,0:17:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我第一次開始說話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次穿上了體育服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被男人看到了裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次進了遊戲中心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.24,0:17:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次被看到了裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天 我第一次交到了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了我是這種怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定她 再也無法做我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算是這樣 我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 史芬克斯！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不聽話的話 我真的要懲罰你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 我們回碰頭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳下...在搖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本理論是Cabala
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要用途是防禦 排除敵對性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽出年代是十六世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有應用性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原始術式裡混合了英國清教術式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言語系統 由希伯來文變更為英語
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.88,0:19:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從術式的構成上看 並不是自動控制 而是遠程操作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TTTR
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.64,0:19:31.52,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<向右歪曲>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CFA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:40.93,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<變更為向上>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PIOBTLL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.43,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<左腳向後方>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用不了魔術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 能讓魔術混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強制詠唱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:57.57,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<Spell Intercept>
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這個在施術者的控制當中搗亂的強制詠唱的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CR　BBF　TTNATWITOD
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.40,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(279,440)}<向右變更>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.40,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(359,440)}<雙足交叉>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.40,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(504,440)}<脖子跟腰呈逆方向旋轉>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.46,0:20:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是巧妙躲開還不足夠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對自我修復術式進行逆運算
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其週期約為3秒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來利用的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.03,0:20:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行得通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,CR
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.04,0:21:03.69,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<向右變更>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MBFPADCOG
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.43,0:21:19.87,*Default3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,440)}<雙腳平行配置 失去重心>
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人把遠程操縱變換成自動控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搗亂不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.31,0:21:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当麻...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.95,0:23:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有新的火種產生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.37,0:23:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會一直...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集 虛數學區·五行機關
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科學與魔術交錯之時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.07,0:23:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事就開始了


